reviews.review_text: this show is great wow, listen to this scarlet>fire!  wonderful, layered, patient playing by everyone.  and this audience tape is so crisp in the highs, yet still has some phil thump!
Best Aud source? I'm going with this one.  A little bass light, with nice mids and highs.
